      <para id="id5207320"/>
      <list id="id2503959" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Design a necklace for Zero that he can show his people on the planet. Use beads, seeds and other interesting articles.</item>
      </list>
    </section>
    <section id="id1168093871392">
      <title>My design:</title>
      <list id="id8359072" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>What are you going to use to make the necklace?</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id6864108">Zero is excited about our beautiful green country. He wants to take some of our plants to his planet. Do you think the plants will grow there? </para>
      <para id="id6091545">Discuss in your groups:</para>
      <list id="id7133426" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Is there water on Mars? </item>
        <item>Do you think the sun shines on Mars? </item>
        <item>Will somebody on the planet know how to look after the plants? </item>
        <item>Do plants need water?</item>
      </list>
    </section>
    <section id="id1168093869069">
      <title>Group work: plan an experiment.</title>
      <para id="id6247989">Remember:</para>
      <list id="id3173597" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>You must use two plants so that you can compare them.</item>
        <item>You must treat them exactly the same except for what you are testing.</item>
        <item>You must record what you notice.</item>
      </list>
      <list id="id6857247" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Draw a picture of what you are going to do:</item>
        <item>What do you think will happen?</item>
      </list>
    </section>
    <section id="id8971588">
      <title>My observations</title>
      <list id="id1168093861887" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>What did happen?</item>
        <item>Would you like to pay a visit to Zero?</item>
        <item>Draw a picture of Zero and his vehicle.</item>
      </list>
    </section>
